        <member name="T:Luolan.QQBot.OneBot.OneBotOptions">
            <summary>
            OneBot 客户端配置选项
            <para>同时支持 OneBot 11 (NapCat/CQHTTP) 和 OneBot 12 (ISO标准) 两种协议</para>
            </summary>
            <example>
            示例 1: NapCat (OneBot 11, 自动检测)
            <code>
            var options = new OneBotOptions
            {
                WebSocketUrl = "ws://127.0.0.1:6700",
                AccessToken = "your_token",
                ProtocolVersion = OneBotVersion.Auto  // 自动检测
            };
            </code>
            
            示例 2: Lagrange (OneBot 12, 显式指定)
            <code>
            var options = new OneBotOptions
            {
                WebSocketUrl = "ws://127.0.0.1:3001",
                ProtocolVersion = OneBotVersion.V12
            };
            </code>
            </example>
        </member>
